    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Red-figure kraters in the form of an inverted bell with handles placed high on the body.  The rim is offset and the foot is stepped.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
